* phase-5 tail: EIS operand descriptors (ADSC/BDSC/VDSC/NDSC).  Each follows an
* EIS instruction (here MLR) which sets the descriptor count and the MF state
* the descriptors read (IDS indexes MF[]).  ADSC9 scales its char offset by 2.
       MLR   0,0
       ADSC4 100,1,5
       ADSC9 200,1,5
       BDSC  300,2,9
       VDSC  50,0,1
       NDSC9 400,0,6,1,0
       END
